response.original_title: GTNA Best Of Both Worlds - 360 vs Kerser
response.overview: The biggest match up in Australian battle rap for 2011. Campbelltown's Kerser goes toe to toe with Melbourne's 360 to settle the hype between their two vocal fanbases. Will this battle decide the winner?
